flowchart LR
    U[Users and Merchants] --> R53[Route 53 DNS Failover]
    R53 --> ALB1[Mumbai ALB + WAF]
    R53 --> ALB2[Hyderabad ALB + WAF]

    subgraph Mumbai ap-south-1
        ALB1 --> EKS1[EKS Payment Services]
        EKS1 --> AUR1[Aurora PostgreSQL Writer]
        EKS1 --> DDB1[DynamoDB Global Table]
        EKS1 --> REDIS1[ElastiCache Redis Primary]
        EKS1 --> MSK1[MSK Kafka Primary]
    end

    subgraph Hyderabad ap-south-2
        ALB2 --> EKS2[EKS Hot Standby Services]
        EKS2 --> AUR2[Aurora PostgreSQL Reader]
        EKS2 --> DDB2[DynamoDB Global Table]
        EKS2 --> REDIS2[ElastiCache Redis Secondary]
        EKS2 --> MSK2[MSK Kafka DR]
    end

    AUR1 -. Aurora Global Database .-> AUR2
    DDB1 <-. Global Tables .-> DDB2
    REDIS1 -. Global Datastore .-> REDIS2
    MSK1 -. MSK Replicator .-> MSK2
